author: Zakhar Kleyman
config:
identifier: logkeeper
command_type: system
post:
- command: gotest.parse_files
  params:
    files:
    - src/*.suite
buildvariants:
- name: ubuntu
  display_name: Ubuntu
  expansions:
    mongo_url: http://fastdl.mongodb.org/linux/mongodb-linux-x86_64-3.2.6.tgz
  run_on:
  - docker
  tasks:
  - name: test
tasks:
- name: test
  commands:
  - command: git.get_project
    params:
      directory: src
  - command: git.apply_patch
    params:
      directory: src
  - command: shell.exec
    params:
      script: |
        set -o errexit
        mkdir mongodb
        cd mongodb
        curl ${mongo_url} -o mongodb.tgz
        tar xvf mongodb.tgz
        chmod +x ./mongodb-*/bin/*
        mv ./mongodb-*/bin/* .
        mkdir -p db_files
  - command: shell.exec
    params:
      background: true
      script: |
        ./mongod --dbpath ./db_files &
      working_dir: mongodb
  - command: shell.exec
    params:
      script: "cd mongodb \n./mongo --nodb --eval 'assert.soon(function(x){try{var
        d = new Mongo(\"localhost:27017\"); return true}catch(e){return false}}, \"timed
        out connecting\")'\n"
      working_dir: mongodb
  - command: shell.exec
    params:
      script: |
        . ./set_gopath.sh
        set -e
        go test -v > logkeeper.suite
      type: test
      working_dir: src
